model

Class Node

  • java.lang.Object
    • model.Node

  • public class Node
extends java.lang.Object
    The Node class are used to indicate paths for the enemies to take. A linked list is created to keep track of the nodes.
    Author:
    Ethan Glasberg (glasberg@email.arizona.edu), Jarod Bristol (jarodkylebristol@email.arizona.edu), Alex Gonzalez (aegonzalez793@email.arizona.edu), Patrick Dearborn (pdearborn@email.arizona.edu)
